data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom, 2 and a half Bathroom home in Baywood Village. Over 2400 square feet, very open floorplan and entertaining fenced backyard for enjoyment! Gorgeous foyer area opens up to Dining room with Coffered ceiling and very Spacious Eat-in-Kitchen which features Granite countertops, Island and Stainless Steel appliances. Hardwood flooring downstairs and carpeting in Living Room with Fireplace. Upstairs has a very nice landing area that opens up to all bedrooms. Master Bedroom has walk in closet and gorgeous Master Bath with Dual Vanity, Separate Shower with glass doors and Garden Tub. Huge Fenced in back yard with Above Ground Pool, Wooden Swing Set and Shed. Solar Panels recently installed! Pets are Negotiable and must be approved by owner, $500 refundable if there is no pet damage or odor. This home is a must see!
